{"tid":1672114,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［區議會文宣］有冇法律/政黨巴絲教吓可以點樣做選舉文宣又唔會害到非建制候選人？","createTime":"2019-10-24T02:14:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T15:07:44.000Z","uid":171094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dce88b27d3c18b3cd3da6f71754a1f1c21416b96","tid":1672114,"uid":171094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T02:14:18.000Z","msg":"區議會就到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再唔準備宣傳或者開始應戰，我哋又會失去一次大好翻盤機會<br />\n依家中聯辦下面嗰啲「九龍社團聯會」「新界社團聯會」「香港島各界聯合會」又出成堆偽獨立，甚至扮黃候選人出嚟選<br />\n好似油尖旺富柏區呢個陳德立實際係「九龍社團聯會」下屬「油青尖旺青年社」同「樂活富柏」 阿頭，同時呢條友又係「關注青年住屋聯席」嘅人，啲組織名好似好關注年青人問題<br />\n又扮到好似泛民組織嘅名咁，實際上只係一直倡議放寛按揭成數，加多首置地咁，完全in line with 政府政策，又係幫手推高樓市出賣青年組織<br />\n<br />\n當時陳凱欣選佢甚至喺埋陳凱欣份宣傳單張上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eqUPQZx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeqUPQZx.jpg&h=28dbac1e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a2Jtm6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa2Jtm6c.jpg&h=90b06dc3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KEa7CEy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKEa7CEy.jpg&h=1bac54d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係我知選舉期間做宣傳有好多規矩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好驚做完一大堆嘢篤爆晒啲偽獨立人嘅嘢之後<br />\n非建制候選人會被人話影響選舉公正<br />\n所以想問下自己出去做文宣有冇啲咩一定唔做得㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望推到有人出嚟教教咁多連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dcadb9a1f8345a84760d35b3cb8fc5894d7ff4e","tid":1672114,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T02:16:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【SUCK／1026】長龍爆買日 - 黃店存貨壓力測試（2）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1672101\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1672101</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V4S58Lb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src