d/1666510\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1666510</a>"},{"pid":"67da6b6c01b0cbb31228f323fb1747c504feed11","tid":1672114,"uid":277897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T15:07:44.000Z","msg":"佢真係九龍社團聯會，大家上官網睇吓，年初落區插旗，打正九龍社團聯會旗號，大家認清楚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h66rS3e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh66rS3e.jpg&h=cd680060&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3mBO6of.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3mBO6of.jpg&h=a28dbee7&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}